_sText: This map is custom created by me, shotgun_master it is free to distribute. Enjoy it and and do NOT claim it as your own work! Them map consists of 18 spawn points, 9 for terrorsists and 9 for counter terrorists. Each spawn team spawn location is located on opposites sides of the map in the middle of the map is two buildings, one for each team to battle it out along with many other barriers. And where the main walk way coming off of each teams spawn meet is a area for the teams to battle, this map was originally designed for gungame!
